NG0519:4: ston pa rdo rje 'chang chen nga *//
NG0519:5: stag spyad ri la ting nge 'dzin //
NG0519:6: lo lnga 'brug gam gnyis bzhugs so //
NG0519:7: de nas 'gro ba'i don la bzhengs //
NG0519:8: tshe lo lnga stong thub pa'i dus //
NG0519:9: lho phyogs bya rgod phung po'i ri //
NG0519:10: nyan thos rnams dang yid 'dres phyir //
NG0519:11: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba'i khab //
NG0519:12: lho phyogs rgyang grag gcig gi sa //
NG0519:13: pha ni rgyal po seng ge bzang *//
NG0519:16: gser 'od dam pa bya bar grags //
NG0519:17: nyan thos rnam pa'i gdung ba gcad //
NG0519:18: glegs bam zhu ma 'di gtad do //
NG0519:20: skad cig rdzogs sangs rgyas 'dod na //
NG0519:21: lus ngag yid gsum bya ba btang *//
NG0519:22: shes pa rtse gcig drang lus gcun //
NG0519:24: byung gnas 'gro gsum brtags pas shes //
NG0519:25: 'dug stangs gsum dang ldan pa na //
NG0519:26: dbyings kyis nang na 'od kyis khyim //
NG0519:27: 'gyur de ye mnyam chen po ni //
NG0519:28: sangs rgyas sems can thams cad la //
NG0519:29: byas pa med par ye mnyam gnas //
NG0519:30: 'di nyid su yi rtogs pa'i mi //
NG0519:31: rang rig ngo bo rtogs pa'o //
NG0519:32: sho lo ka ni bdun pa 'di //
NG0519:33: thugs rje dran sangs rgyas pa ste //
NG0519:34: skal ldan bu la rims kyis gtod //
NG0519:35: skal med rnams la ma nye zhig / sngags kyi srungs mas thub par srungs //
